unicef-mnh4.def: Percentage of women aged 20 24 who gave birth before age 18. The indicator refers to women who had a live birth in a recent time period, generally two years for MICS and five years for DHS.
unicef-mnh4.name: Births by age 18
unicef-mnh4.source: DHS, MICS and other national household surveys. Last update: January 2021.
unicef-mnh4.dataset: DHS, MICS and other national household surveys. Last update: January 2021.
